    "paragraphs": [
        "",
        "The world of business includes a wide variety of career fields, so our department offers a broad selection of degree plans that are flexible enough to fit your specific interests.",
        "Whichever one you choose, you will gain the real-world knowledge and skills you need to succeed in your career. You will also engage with the local business community for practical experience that will give you a head start once you graduate.",
        "Refer to theUndergraduate Catalogfor a full list of Minors and their requirements.",
        "The Norris-Vincent College of Business is accredited by AACSB International.",
        "Oct 4",
        "May 3",
        "May 2",
        "Today\u2019s world is driven by business, trade and commerce. Your ASU degree is your ticket to join the exciting and dynamic global marketplace and help shape the future of business, healthcare and government.",
        "Take a look at some other aspects of our department that make ASU an outstanding place to study management and marketing.",
        "You can engage with professionals at local businesses, firms and nonprofit agencies through internships and shadowing programs, and in our Small Business Development Center. You can also enhance your practical skills in our student BizPitch Contest and/or the San Angelo Business Plan Competition.",
        "Our chapter of the Delta Sigma Pi national professional business fraternity has won multiple national awards, including the 2018-19 Outstanding Collegiate Chapter Award. It is open to all students in our department.",
        "All of the B.B.A. and MBA degree programs in our department are accredited by AACSB International. That means you are getting the highest-quality education possible.",
